                                <h3>The Next Generation of HCASH</h3>
                                <p>- A parallel, dual-chain ecosystem</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bd">
                            <div class="article2">
                                <p>The HCASH network has two chains running laterally, with each serving different functions within the ecosystem. These two chains serve to provide us with an interlinked, bifocal dual-token, dual-chain ecosystem that will help us solve interconnection, privacy and security issues prevalent in the current blockchain ecosystem.</p>
                                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                                <p>The HCASH ecosystem will consist of two chains that include the HyperCash (HC) main chain and the HyperExchange (HX) chain that is derived from the main chain, but will work towards bridging communication between blockchains including BTC, ETH and others, and non-blockchains such as DAGs</p>
                            </div>
